OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCost of living: Firms      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fwarned consumers want more 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fthan low prices            
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Six in 10 consumers say low prices will
OL,6, become more influential when choosing  
OL,7, where to shop and what to buy in the   
OL,8, next two years, a survey has suggested.
OL,10,FBut businesses need to offer more than 
OL,11,Fjust discounts to customers, according 
OL,12,Fto the Institute of Customer Service.  
OL,14,FThe organisation, which surveyed 10,000
OL,15,Fpeople, said firms should offer value  
OL,16,Fand a choice of ways to pay.           
OL,18,FAbout a third of those asked were still
OL,19,Fprepared to pay more to guarantee good 
OL,20,Fservice.                               
